<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in; text-align:center"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri"><strong>THE EFFECT OF RADIATION</strong></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">Some experts suggests that little radiation is good in terms of medical x-ray to combat and diagnose </span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">illness in our body. It is only these experts that will know how much is little such as our bodies can </span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri">tolerate. To layman, it is dangerous to expose our bodies to radiation.</span></span></p>

